title in 20 years, reached the fastest lap of one minute, 19.476 
seconds late in the rainy afternoon session that saw many drivers 
struggling to stay on track. 
</P>
<P>
	``The car was good right from the start and we made at least two  
major steps forward,'' Irvine said. 
</P>
<P>
