<HEADLINE> Penguins Sign Center Straka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PITTSBURGH (AP) -- The Pittsburgh Penguins avoided contract  
arbitration Friday by signing center Martin Straka to a $3.4 
million, two-year contract. 
</P>
