since rejoining the Penguins in 1997. He first played for 
Pittsburgh from 1992-95, then was traded to Ottawa and later played 
for the New York Islanders and Florida Panthers before re-signing 
with Pittsburgh as a free agent. 
</P>
<P>
	A native of the Czech Republic, he was the Penguins' first-round  
draft choice in 1992. 
</P>
