<HEADLINE> Galaxy Reacquire Salcedo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PASADENA, Calif. (AP) -- The Los Angeles Galaxy reacquired  
midfielder Jorge Salcedo from the Tampa Bay Mutiny on Friday for 
midfielder Daniel Hernandez. 
</P>
<P>
	Salcedo, 26, had one assist in 16 games for Tampa Bay, and one  
goal and five assists in 15 games last season after being acquired 
from the Chicago Fire on June 29, 1998. 
</P>
