traded to the Colorado Rapids on Feb. 1, 1997, for the first pick 
in Major League Soccer's supplemental draft. 
</P>
<P>
	Hernandez, 24, played in 12 games for the Galaxy this season. He  
was the team's second-round draft pick in the 1998 MLS draft after 
playing at Southern Methodist. 
